txt.en: Collect materials to build a door that will defend the upper level of Lugazag. All the materials needed can be found in the wilds of the Ettenmoors.
'We cannot rest. The enemy will return to take the tower and we must defend the upper levels. Make your way into the Ettenmoors and collect the materials needed to construct the interior door.'
'These are good materials and will build a sturdy gate. We will put these to use immediately.\n\n'Thank you.'
Collect materials to build a gate that will prevent the enemy from breaching the upper level at the tower of Lugazag.
'Do not rest. We need to defend the tower.'
